# Xellar-Kit Package Structure

The main Xellar-Kit package is organized as follows:

## Core Components

- **src/components/** - UI components including the Connect Button and dialogs
- **src/providers/** - React providers including the main XellarKitProvider
- **src/hooks/** - React hooks for integrating with wallets and UI state
- **src/config/** - Configuration utilities and defaults
- **src/styles/** - Theming and styling

## Key Files

- [packages/xellar-kit/src/components/connect-button/connect-button.tsx](mdc:packages/xellar-kit/src/components/connect-button/connect-button.tsx) - Main button component for wallet connections
- [packages/xellar-kit/src/providers/xellar-kit.tsx](mdc:packages/xellar-kit/src/providers/xellar-kit.tsx) - Main provider component
- [packages/xellar-kit/src/config/default-config.ts](mdc:packages/xellar-kit/src/config/default-config.ts) - Default configuration

## Entry Point

The main entry point [packages/xellar-kit/src/index.ts](mdc:packages/xellar-kit/src/index.ts) exports all public APIs.
